      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPRING MAISIE (2) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (20.23) at this track in a Grade 6. Has first look at box 2 this time. Goes very well at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. Rates highly and will give a great sight. ATOMIC PRINCE (1) finished third last time (22.08) at this track after winning at his previous two outings. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Will give a great sight again. HOLD AND SPIN (3) turned in a moderate run last time when seventh at this track over 457m behind Spartan (26.41) in a Grade 6/MDN. Was in the money the start prior. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can do much better this time. HARA'S GREGOR (5) cannot be left out after placing last start.",
